WEBVTT

00:01.165 --> 00:04.132
Sammy, it's me.

00:06.637 --> 00:08.670
I don't remember most
of what Michael did

00:08.672 --> 00:11.673
because I was underwater,
drowning...

00:11.675 --> 00:13.508
and that I remember.

00:13.510 --> 00:16.044
I felt every second
of it.

00:16.046 --> 00:18.580
Why would Michael
give up his vessel like that?

00:18.582 --> 00:20.482
I don't know.

00:20.484 --> 00:23.318
- Ghosts 101.
- Ghost possession.

00:23.320 --> 00:24.920
Definitely a ghost.

00:24.922 --> 00:26.154
Somebody's spirit
can attach itself

00:26.156 --> 00:27.689
to an object
or a bunch of objects.

00:27.691 --> 00:29.357
Everything has a weakness.

00:29.359 --> 00:31.660
They hate
iron and salt.

00:31.662 --> 00:34.096
Whatever happens,
you stay inside this circle.

00:38.402 --> 00:40.569
- Where's the spear?!
- So Michael wants the spear

00:40.571 --> 00:42.504
because he knows
it can hurt him.

00:42.506 --> 00:43.438
You're no different
than him.

00:43.440 --> 00:45.006
I am nothing like him.

00:47.544 --> 00:49.111
<i>Do you</i>
<i>have unwanted gold</i>

00:49.113 --> 00:51.246
<i>just lying around the house,</i>
<i>collecting dust?</i>

00:51.248 --> 00:53.582
<i>Why not turn that gold</i>
<i>into cash?</i>

00:53.584 --> 00:55.117
<i>Here at Diamond Dave's,</i>

00:55.119 --> 00:57.085
<i>you can have cash</i>
<i>in your hands today.</i>

00:57.087 --> 00:58.954
<i>We'll take anything</i>
<i>you want to sell us.</i>

00:58.956 --> 01:00.922
<i>When Aunt Gloria</i>
<i>passed away,</i>

01:00.924 --> 01:03.291
<i>she left me so much jewelry,</i>
<i>I didn't know what to do.</i>

01:03.293 --> 01:05.126
<i>That's when I called</i>
<i>Diamond Dave.</i>

01:05.129 --> 01:07.696
<i>If it's gold,</i>
<i>it's cash in your hands.</i>

01:07.698 --> 01:10.932
<i>You're watching Shocker TV.</i>

01:12.736 --> 01:16.238
<i>This week on Shocker,</i>
<i>it's gonna be a blood bath.</i>

01:16.240 --> 01:18.573
<i>We've got slicing and dicing.</i>

01:18.575 --> 01:21.376
<i>We've got scream queens</i>
<i>and killing machines,</i>

01:21.378 --> 01:24.079
<i>24 hours a day, all week long.</i>

01:24.081 --> 01:27.215
<i>Time to slice and dice.</i>

01:57.681 --> 01:59.815
Whoa.

01:59.817 --> 02:02.951
Mezco 15" Mega-Scale Panthro.

02:02.953 --> 02:04.486
So handsome.

02:04.488 --> 02:06.354
So angry.

02:31.215 --> 02:32.480
Hey, Sam.

02:32.482 --> 02:34.382
<i>Stuart,</i>
<i>what did you do?</i>

02:34.384 --> 02:35.650
I...

02:35.652 --> 02:36.952
Uh, nothing.

02:36.954 --> 02:38.520
<i>Really?</i>

02:38.522 --> 02:40.222
<i>Because according to Yelp</i>

02:40.224 --> 02:43.358
<i>and this awesome,</i>
<i>one-star review we just got,</i>

02:43.360 --> 02:46.962
<i>you screamed at a customer</i>
<i>and called him a, quote,</i>

02:46.964 --> 02:50.565
<i>"mongoloid Tribble</i>
<i>in a robotic exoskeleton</i>

02:50.567 --> 02:53.301
<i>built by Tony Stark's</i>
<i>inbred third cousin."</i>

02:53.303 --> 02:54.836
<i>Which is not cool,</i>

02:54.838 --> 02:56.905
<i>and weirdly,</i>
<i>creepily specific.</i>

02:56.907 --> 02:59.574
That --

02:59.576 --> 03:01.409
He said I couldn't
beat up Superman.

03:01.411 --> 03:04.746
<i>Okay. Again,</i>
<i>Superman is not real.</i>

03:04.748 --> 03:06.381
Okay.
That's not the point.

03:06.383 --> 03:08.149
<i>And I have seen you</i>
<i>get winded eating a taco.</i>

03:08.151 --> 03:09.684
Okay, that doesn't matter.

03:09.686 --> 03:11.920
If I had kryptonite gloves,
I could beat up Superman.

03:11.922 --> 03:14.756
Anyone could.
That's science, Sam.

03:14.758 --> 03:18.426
<i>Look, I --</i>
<i>I like that you care --</i>

03:18.428 --> 03:20.328
<i>really, really care</i>
<i>about this stuff,</i>

03:20.330 --> 03:23.531
<i>but we need every customer</i>
<i>we can get, okay?</i>

03:23.533 --> 03:27.302
<i>So just chill</i>
<i>a little, please.</i>

03:29.706 --> 03:31.840
Yeah, um...

03:31.842 --> 03:34.042
Okay.

03:34.044 --> 03:37.779
I'm sorry, Sam. I just --
I just get spun out sometimes.

03:37.781 --> 03:40.115
<i>I know.</i>

03:40.117 --> 03:41.383
Coming to game night?

03:41.385 --> 03:43.351
<i>Of course.</i>

03:43.353 --> 03:45.186
<i>I'll see you there.</i>

04:19.990 --> 04:24.559
Yeah, well,
all I'm hearing is excuses.

04:24.561 --> 04:28.797
Okay, look, I don't
care about traffic, okay?!

04:28.799 --> 04:31.433
It has been
over 30 minutes, so --

04:31.435 --> 04:32.801
Hello?!

04:32.803 --> 04:35.270
Free pizza!

04:48.518 --> 04:49.851
The heck?

04:54.858 --> 04:55.991
H-How did you...

05:03.767 --> 05:07.767
<b><font color="#00FF00">♪ Supernatural 14x04 ♪</font></b>
<font color="#00FFFF">Mint Condition</font>
